            <p>Aatura Hospital's Neurosurgery Department is equipped with state-of-the-art surgical facilities, advanced imaging technology, and intraoperative navigation systems to ensure the highest standards of precision, safety, and outcomes in neurosurgical care. Our operating rooms are equipped with specialized neurosurgical instruments, microscopes, and neuroimaging tools to support complex surgical procedures.</p>
        </div>
